\f0\fs24 \cf0 # API Troubleshooting Assistant\
\
AI-powered assistant for system analysts and support teams that helps process customer API issues faster.\
\
## Problem\
\
System analysts often receive customer emails about API errors. To respond, they need to search documentation, troubleshooting cases, previous incidents, and known issues manually.\
\
## Solution\
\
API Troubleshooting Assistant analyzes a customer message, finds similar troubleshooting cases, suggests possible root causes, and generates a draft response to the customer.\
\
## MVP Features\
\
- Paste customer email or ticket text\
- Detect API endpoint, error code, and issue summary\
- Search similar troubleshooting cases\
- Suggest possible solutions\
- Generate customer-friendly email draft\
\
## Tech Stack\
\
- Python\
- Streamlit\
- OpenAI API\
- ChromaDB\
- CSV knowledge base}